descriptionHtml:
This is still in progress

The new Helgen It is a town.. or village that allows people of any race live there
Orcs, Dunmer, Khajits, Nords, etc..
for that reason i tried to make something like 3 sectors
One with a Orc strongholds, other sector with building for Elf and khajits and another for nords, imperials, bretons and redguards...
in other sector i placed 3 temples; Dunmer temple... Malacath temple and julianos temple ( maybe i make a temple if i have time for khajits )

in the town there's not people yet... cuz i have real problems with the cr@ps AI packages it never works for me. but if someone want to help me with that i will be glad or be patience and when i finally get it i'll place peoplen and other things



V 0.2 the town now is divided in districts
Orcs : Stonghold, blacksmith and houses
Elf : Houses, 2 little farms, central house and market
Nords, Impirials, Bretons and Red Guards : Inn, Stables, Market and houses
Khajits and Argonians : Market, Watch tower (looking for buildings, there's no one yet)
Keep and temples: Keep (not edited yet) Malacath temple, Dunmer Temple, Julianos Temple

All the districts have markets but ther's not people yet

Note: you will need; Latest Skyrim version 1.932 and DLC Dragonborn

Note2: Sorry for my poor english
